<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,1951,2014]" lastBlockId="9.[151,1436,152,251]" lastPageId="9" lastPageNumber="164" pageId="8" pageNumber="163">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,729,1951,1978]" pageId="8" pageNumber="163">
Justification of the synonymy of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gawande &amp; Bodkhe" authorityYear="2018" box="[593,722,1952,1978]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Scopoides" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="8" pageNumber="163" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="samarae">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[593,609,1952,1978]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="163">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[624,722,1952,1978]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="163">samarae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Judging from the original genitalic illustrations of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gawande &amp; Bodkhe" authorityYear="2018" box="[1311,1436,1952,1978]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Scopoides" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="8" pageNumber="163" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="samarae">
<emphasis box="[1311,1325,1952,1978]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="163">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1340,1436,1953,1978]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="163">samarae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Gawande, B. &amp; Bodkhe, A." box="[159,460,1988,2014]" pageId="8" pageNumber="163" pagination="223 - 228" refId="ref4280" refString="Gawande, B. &amp; Bodkhe, A. (2018) Description of spider genus Scopoides as a new species (Araneae: Gnaphosidae) from Wari Reserve Forest Area, Maharashtra, India. In: Rao, P. N., Saxena, A., Pandey, B. N. &amp; Kulkarni, G. K. (Eds.), Biodiversity and bioprospects: Indian scenario and perspectives. Today &amp; Tomorrow's Printers and Publishers, New Delhi, pp. 223 - 228." type="book chapter" year="2018">Gawande &amp; Bodkhe 2018</bibRefCitation>
: figs 5–6), it is clear that this species has all diagnostic features of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Tikader" authorityYear="1982" box="[1224,1338,1988,2014]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Drassodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="8" pageNumber="163" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="luridus">
<emphasis box="[1224,1244,1989,2014]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="163">D</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1259,1338,1988,2014]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="163">luridus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as mentioned under the synonymy of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Tikader &amp; Gajbe" authorityYear="1977" box="[500,638,153,179]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Scopodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="164" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maitraiae">
<emphasis box="[500,514,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="164">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[529,638,154,179]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="164">maitraiae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(compare 
<bibRefCitation author="Gawande, B. &amp; Bodkhe, A." box="[760,1059,153,179]" pageId="9" pageNumber="164" pagination="223 - 228" refId="ref4280" refString="Gawande, B. &amp; Bodkhe, A. (2018) Description of spider genus Scopoides as a new species (Araneae: Gnaphosidae) from Wari Reserve Forest Area, Maharashtra, India. In: Rao, P. N., Saxena, A., Pandey, B. N. &amp; Kulkarni, G. K. (Eds.), Biodiversity and bioprospects: Indian scenario and perspectives. Today &amp; Tomorrow's Printers and Publishers, New Delhi, pp. 223 - 228." type="book chapter" year="2018">Gawande &amp; Bodkhe 2018</bibRefCitation>
: figs 5–6 with 
<bibRefCitation author="Tikader, B. K." box="[1228,1382,153,179]" pageId="9" pageNumber="164" pagination="295 - 536" refId="ref4634" refString="Tikader, B. K. (1982) Family Gnaphosidae. Fauna India, 3 (Araneae), 295 - 536." type="journal article" year="1982">Tikader 1982</bibRefCitation>
: figs 261–262 and 
<bibRefCitation author="Caleb, J. T. D. &amp; Karthikeyani, R. &amp; Muthuchelian, K." box="[302,781,189,215]" pageId="9" pageNumber="164" pagination="135 - 138" refId="ref4147" refString="Caleb, J. T. D., Karthikeyani, R. &amp; Muthuchelian, K. (2014) Description of Drassodes luridus O. P. Cambridge (Araneae: Gnaphosidae): First record from Tamil Nadu, India. Journal of Entomology and Zoology Studies, 2, 135 - 138." type="journal article" year="2014">Caleb, Karthikeyani &amp; Muthuchelian 2014</bibRefCitation>
: fig. 1e–f). The species 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gawande &amp; Bodkhe" authorityYear="2018" box="[1043,1166,189,215]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Scopoides" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="164" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="samarae">
<emphasis box="[1043,1057,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="164">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1070,1166,190,215]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="164">samarae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
should thus be regarded as a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Tikader" authorityYear="1982" box="[415,528,225,251]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Drassodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="164" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="luridus">
<emphasis box="[415,435,226,251]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="164">D</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[449,528,225,251]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="164">luridus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
